<p><img src="https://www.chiefdelphi.com/uploads/default/original/3X/3/7/37c7755d654f3a975ed492dfce55f8e43fca2d74.png" alt="image" data-base62-sha1="7XrB7cf0ulEQRMjAppR6JV62Xl2" width="238" height="24"></p>
<p>I think it makes sense to divide. In our case, the gear ratio is approximately ~21 which means that the driven gear is ~21 times slower than the driving gear. So, if the motor can do ~100 rev/s, that would mean the wheel could do ~21 times less, which is right about ~4 rev/s.</p>","post_number":7,"post_type":1,"posts_count":9,"updated_at":"2025-02-14T13:31:29.717Z","reply_count":1,"reply_to_post_number":6,"quote_count":0,"incoming_link_count":1,"reads":72,"readers_count":71,"score":39.4,"yours":false,"topic_id":491642,"topic_slug":"yagsl-calculates-our-max-ang-velocity-to-be-12000rad-s","display_username":"Andrii Bessarab","primary_group_name":null,"flair_name":null,"flair_url":null,"flair_bg_color":null,"flair_color":null,"flair_group_id":null,"badges_granted":[],"version":1,"can_edit":false,"can_delete":false,"can_recover":false,"can_see_hidden_post":true,"can_wiki":false,"read":true,"user_title":null,"reply_to_user":{"id":51887,"username":"nstrike","name":"","avatar_template":"/user_avatar/www.chiefdelphi.com/nstrike/{size}/167038_2.png"},"bookmarked":false,"actions_summary":[{"id":2,"count":1}],"moderator":false,"admin":false,"staff":false,"user_id":58460,"hidden":false,"trust_level":1,"deleted_at":null,"user_deleted":false,"edit_reason":null,"can_view_edit_history":true,"wiki":false,"user_custom_fields":{"user_field_4":"4951 Alumni"},"post_url":"/t/yagsl-calculates-our-max-ang-velocity-to-be-12000rad-s/491642/7","custom_user_title":"4951 Alumni","reactions":[{"id":"heart","type":"emoji","count":1}],"current_user_reaction":null,"reaction_users_count":1,"current_user_used_main_reaction":false,"can_accept_answer":false,"can_unaccept_answer":false,"accepted_answer":false,"topic_accepted_answer":true},{"id":3527005,"name":"","username":"nstrike","avatar_template":"/user_avatar/www.chiefdelphi.com/nstrike/{size}/167038_2.png","created_at":"2025-02-14T14:28:20.050Z","cooked":"<p>Yep that does seem more correct! I will push this change along with the next official r